Online Mode: Gate won't open by itself. If someone passes through, it will send a gate opening request to the server (through SDK connection or active connection to TCP server) Only when the server authorized can the gate be opened.
In the following options: if "release all" is selected, all opening requests will be responded If "disable all" is selected, all opening requests are rejected If "self determination" is selected, an option dialog box will pop up
